data.description: Gorgeous 3 bed 2.5 bath home with 2 car garage & beautiful mountain views. All new two tone interior paint. Open concept kitchen features stunning granite counter-tops, beautiful cabinets with plenty of storage & built-in pantry closet. Seller will provide new stainless steel appliances including gas range, OTR microwave & dishwasher prior to closing. Spacious floor plan with ceramic tile flooring throughout entire downstairs & laundry & bathrooms upstairs. Plush new carpet & pad in all the bedrooms & loft. Large master suite with walk-in closet. Master bathroom has dual sink vanity, garden tub, walk-in shower, & private toilet room. Great curb appeal with easy care landscaping featuring trees & deco rock. Back yard features covered patio. Move in ready, come see it today! Agent/Owner.
